                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-22-defend269 t17830115-22-punish147"></join>
               To be publickly whipped
            </rs> and <rs id="t17830115-22-punish148" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830115-22-punish148" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830115-22-punish148" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="hardLabour"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-22-defend269 t17830115-22-punish148"></join>
               confined to hard labour for 6 months in the house of correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
